1.title: Tea and ...

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: Late-middle-aged Dennis wakes up to discover Zach, an attractive young man in his bed. Is Zach just a one-night stand, or is it more than that? In the opening episode of "How It All Began," watch as Zach and Dennis get to know each other the morning after and test the waters.

2.title: A Night at the Theatre

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

2.plot: Zach and Dennis made plans to see "Outside Mullingar," but Zach screwed it up. They try again when Dennis gets the couple tickets to see Arthur Miller's iconic "Death of Salesman." But once again, things don't turn out as planned - but maybe better.

3.title: The Morning After the Night Before

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

3.plot: After an unexpectedly interesting night at the theatre, Dennis wakes up to try to sort things out with Zach, but a surprise may ruin everything.

4.title: The Barber of Da Ville

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

4.plot: In Episode 4, Dennis was surprised to get a phone call from his ex-, Luke, wanting to meet for dinner. On the date of, Dennis confides in Miles, his barber/therapist, who does his best to make Dennis look dapper.

5.title: After-Math

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

5.plot: Dennis picks Zach up at the hospital after a violent shakeup. Zach asks to spend the night at Dennis' flat, but they walk in to find another surprise at home waiting for them.

6.title: Dinner for Two

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: A few days later, while Zach recuperates at Dennis's house, Luke and Dennis finally have their dinner together; but things don't work out quite as Luke had hoped (and it doesn't help that uninvited guests show up).

7.title: Star Wars

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: Zach and Dennis return from a party, quarreling about "Star Wars," but is that really what the fight is about? And does Zach want his relationship with Dennis to grow?

8.title: Friends W/O Benefits

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

8.plot: Zach patched things up with Dennis, and they seem to be sailing along fine -- but Faye and Miles (who's given her a whole new look) are on the lookout for icebergs...

9.title: Three Guys Walk Into A Bar...

episode of.title: Zach & Dennis: How It All Began (TV Series 2016– )

9.plot: Zach is furious that Dennis is helping fund Luke's movie, sure that it means that the two of them are still involved personally. Will this be the final straw for Zach, or will Dennis be able to convince him otherwise?
